Space Decrypter Officer

[Link to Repo](https://github.com/leelawryanto264-afk/SDO)

About
Earth has received a series of encrypted alien transmissions.
As a newly appointed Space Decrypter Officer, your mission is to decipher every transmission.
Each successful transmission uncovers another piece of the story while introducing a new cipher system to master.
Developed for the 2026 Stardance Challenge

---

Installation

git clone https://github.com/leelawryanto264-afk/SDO
install npm
node main.js

---

Features

- 10 story-driven transmissions
- Caesar, Atbash, Morse, Binary, and Vigenere ciphers
- Tracks progress using SQLite
- Unlockable cipher handbook
- Officer ranks and transmission logs

---

Slack Commands

/sdo-transmission - View current transmission
/sdo-answer - Submit your answer
/sdo-hint - View a hint
/sdo-handbook - View unlocked cipher information
/sdo-log - View decoded transmissions
/sdo-profile - View rank and progress

---

How to Play

1.  Run /sdo-transmission
2.  Decode the message
3.  Submit answer with /sdo-answer
4.  Use /sdo-hint or /sdo-handbook if needed
5.  Type /sdo-log to see past transmissions and /sdo-profile to check stats
6.  Complete all transmissions

